## pinctrl-names

A list of strings providing names for the pin control states indexed by `pinctrl-N` properties.

```dts
/* arch/arm64/boot/dts/qcom/sm8550.dtsi */
uart7: serial@880000 {
    pinctrl-names = "default", "sleep";
    pinctrl-0 = <&qup_uart7_default>;
    pinctrl-1 = <&qup_uart7_sleep>;
};
```
